name: There Out There, How Do I Get To Them
description:
Some days, many days. It just isn’t clear. 
Is it time to move forward or is it time to pause? I don’t have an answer, but I know they’re out there. 
Do we go to them or do they come to us? Many questions with no response. 
In due time.

350 dpi
PNG 6300x4200
